# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:68
msgid ""
"Interpolated values are calculated linear (each step value is equal). Icon: :"
"guilabel:`Diamond`."
msgstr ""
"Interpolerte verdier beregnes lineært (hver trinnverdi er lik). Ikon: :"
"guilabel:`Diamant`."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:69
msgid "Constant"
msgstr "Konstant"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../animation.rst:69
msgid ""
"Interpolated values stay the same until the next key frame, and jump to the "
"new value. Icon: :guilabel:`Square`."
msgstr ""
"Interpolerte verdier forblir de samme til neste nøkkelbilde, og hopper til "
"den nye verdien. Ikon: :guilabel:`Firkant`."

